<Usage of blink_hdd>

1. untar file on root directory (/root/blink_hdd/)
	# have to untar here. 
2. scan all disks and jbods ($sh scan)
3. find where is a disk ($./blink_xx.py -w disk_name)
	# have to choose a proper script for each Snode. 
	# for EPC pod1-12 -> blink_v2.py
	# for EPC pod13~ -> blink_jb7.py
4. blink the disk ($./blink_xx.py -o disk_name)
5. unblink the disk ($./blink_xx.py -f disk_name)
6. blink all disks ($sh blink_all)

Thanks for using this tool.
by shibaboy
